<chapter id="introduction" >
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>
        &pvfViewer; is used to open, view, and print pattern files using the PC Stitch Pattern Viewer
        format.  These files can be obtained from the <ulink url="https://www.patternsonline.com">PatternsOnline</ulink> website.
    </para>
    <para>
        Please report any problems or feature requests to the &pvfViewer; KDE mailing list pvfviewer@kde.org,
        you can subscribe <ulink url="https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/pvfviewer">here</ulink> or
        the KDE bug tracking system at <ulink url="https://bugs.kde.org/">https://bugs.kde.org/</ulink>.
    </para>
    <para>
        The pvfViewer home page is at <ulink url="https://userbase.kde.org/pvfViewer">https://userbase.kde.org/pvfViewer</ulink>
    </para>
</chapter>
